These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, adventure, satire
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, indie, r&b
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, skateboarding, snowboarding
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, roller
1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the fan of indie is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
6. the fan of r&b is the person driving the roller##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2       |     3      |
| Movie-Genre           | scientific        | adventure     | satire    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b      | dubstep     | indie |
| Sport         | skateboarding | snowboarding | handball   |
| Transport     | roller        | jet-ski      | bus        |

