.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, house, punk
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, dancing, drawing
3 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goldfish
3 different games are played: backgammon, whist, chess
1. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the owner of the frog and the fan of techno##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is the fan of techno##1
4. the fan of techno is on the right of the person playing chess##1
5. the fan of techno is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |      3      |
| Music-Genre    | house    | punk | techno |
| Hobby       | dancing   | drawing  | collecting  |
| Pet         | frog      | fish     | goldfish    |
| Game   | backgammon | chess    | whist        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, video-games
There 3 different types of food: papaya, corn, pepper
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, crime, documentary
3 different pets are kept: bird, lizard, rat
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person eating papaya is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the bird and the person eating pepper##2
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
5. the person watching crime movies is the person watching crime movies##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |
| Hobby         | video-games | board-games | drawing |
| Food           | pepper     | corn    | papaya |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | documentary     | crime |
| Pet           | rat         | lizard      | bird    |

