.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, train, airplane
There 3 different types of food: carrot, kiwi, zucchini
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, singing, writing
3 different pets are kept: rat, lizard, horse
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating zucchini is between the owner of the horse and the person eating carrot##2
7. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Transport      | train | van       | airplane   |
| Food          | carrot   | zucchini   | kiwi     |
| Hobby         | singing  | puzzles    | writing  |
| Pet   | lizard | rat | horse |

