.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, lemon, pomegranate
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, iced-tea, 7up
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, mauve, light-blue
1. the person eating asparagus is the person who likes green##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
4. the person eating asparagus is the person who likes green##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
6. the person eating asparagus is the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the person watching action movies is between the person who likes light-blue and the person drinking iced-tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |      3       |
| Food          | asparagus | lemon    | pomegranate  |
| Beverage           | iced-tea      | sprite  | 7up |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | action   | time-travel  |
| Color           | green      | mauve | light-blue        |

