.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-7::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, february, december
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, chef, electrician
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, taxi, van
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, rugby, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the chef##1
2. the accountant is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
4. the person driving the taxi is in the middle##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
6. the accountant is the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
8. the person driving the car is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2       |     3      |
| Birthday   | january         | december      | february   |
| Job        | electrician | chef          | accountant |
| Transport        | car         | taxi        | van       |
| Sport      | rugby       | skateboarding | golf       |

