.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-8::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, photography, woodworking
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, iris, marigold
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, aristoff, bolivar
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, trike
1. the person who growsmarigold is the person driving the bus##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person driving the trike##1
6. the person who growsmarigold is the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2     |      3      |
| Hobby       | woodworking | baking    | photography |
| Flower         | poppy   | iris | marigold     |
| Cigar         | aristoff  | bolivar     | havana        |
| Transport   | trike       | jet-ski   | bus         |

