.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-10::.
City: venice, boston, hannover
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, weightlifting, hannover-polo
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, classical, d&b
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, russian, thai
1. the person who's sport is hannover-polo is on the far left##1
2. the russian is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
3. the russian is the russian##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the fan of classical is the person traveling to venice##1
6. the person traveling to boston is between the argentine and the russian##2
7. the fan of d&b is the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| City      | hannover     | boston | venice  |
| Sport          | hannover-polo   | weightlifting     | biathlon  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | blues    | classical |
| Nationality   | argentine | thai     | russian   |

