.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-11::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, sports, comedy
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, fuchsia, brown
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, golf, rugby
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, tram, trike
1. the person who likes fuchsia is between the person watching comedy movies and the person who likes light-blue##2
2. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
6. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Movie-Genre       | comedy   | sports | epic  |
| Color         | brown      | fuchsia      | light-blue   |
| Sport       | golf      | rugby       | baseball |
| Transport   | quad-bike | trike       | tram     |

