.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-12::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, taxi, ship
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, librarian, manager
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, drama, sports
City: nizza, prague, san-francisco
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the manager##3
6. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1
7. the person watching drama movies is between the engineer and the librarian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Transport          | ship | tram | taxi |
| Job           | engineer   | manager   | librarian |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | drama     | disaster  |
| City   | prague     | san-francisco  | nizza   |

