.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, german, spanish
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, july, april
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, puzzles
3 different pets are kept: bird, frog, goat
1. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in july##2
2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the german is the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the bird##2
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the japanese##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2      |      3      |
| Nationality   | german | spanish    | japanese |
| Birthday       | july          | april     | february       |
| Hobby      | puzzles       | card-games | board-games |
| Pet        | frog          | goat       | bird        |

