There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, soy-milk
3 different pets are kept: cat, rat, turtle
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, handball
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
6. the person who's sport is handball is the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Transport   | scooter     | bike   | quad-bike   |
| Beverage   | coffee   | soy-milk | sprite |
| Pet           | cat        | turtle    | rat       |
| Sport         | basketball | cycling   | handball  |

