.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, water
There are 3 different nationalities: american, australian, canadian
House: ranch-style, art-deco, futuristic
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, daffodil, daisy
1. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the australian is the art-deco house##1
3. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
5. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
6. the futuristic house is between the canadian and the australian##2
7. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | water    | lemonade   | fanta      |
| Nationality   | canadian | american   | australian |
| House           | ranch-style      | futuristic      | art-deco      |
| Flower         | aconite | daisy | daffodil      |

