3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
5. the victorian house is between the person who's hobby is reading and the futuristic house##2
6. the person watching western movies is the futuristic house##1
7. the victorian house is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

