The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, martial-arts, sports
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, surfing
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, collecting, drawing
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's hobby is baking##2
2. the swisher-smoker is the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
7. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Cigar      | fonseca    | oliveros        | swisher |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | martial-arts | sports  |
| Sport         | handball  | biathlon     | surfing |
| Hobby     | baking      | drawing   | collecting    |

