.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, mirinda
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, blues, pop
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, february, september
3 different pets are kept: ferret, horse, turtle
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
4. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
8. the person who's birthday is in february is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda | juice  | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre           | dubstep  | pop  | blues      |
| Birthday   | september | february | april     |
| Pet           | turtle  | ferret | horse         |

 